Version 0.2
-----------
* Version 0.1.1 below existed for quite some time with different commits happening
* But the vdifsim version number was only bumped right before tagging 2.9
* Version for DiFX-2.9

Version 0.1.1
-------------
* Fix issue where the program generates 1 second too much data
* SEFD is an option on command line
* Allow random number seed to be supplied
* Handles LSB for real and complex data
* Include switched power and pcal
* Fix some bugs that avoid possible uninitialised variables
* Allow 16 bit VDIF to be simulated

